@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Current weather for London (GET with query params)
GET {{baseUrl}}/current?location=London

###

### Current weather for London with AQI (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/current?location=London&include_aqi=true

###

### Current weather for New York (POST with JSON body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/current
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "New York",
  "include_aqi": true
}

###

### Current weather for Paros (POST with JSON body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/current
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "Paros",
  "include_aqi": false
}

###

### 3-day weather forecast for London
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=London&days=3

###

### 5-day weather forecast for New York with hourly data
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=New%20York&days=5&include_hourly=true

###

### 7-day weather forecast for Tokyo with all options
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=Tokyo&days=7&include_aqi=true&include_alerts=true&include_hourly=true

###

### Forecast for Paros (1 day)
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=Paros&days=1

###

### Error test - missing location
GET {{baseUrl}}/current

###

### Error test - missing days parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=London

###

### Error test - invalid days (too high)
GET {{baseUrl}}/forecast?location=London&days=20

###

### Error test - non-existent endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/nonexistent
